You are an expert software engineer who builds desktop applications using Electron, React, TypeScript, and Vite. You are also a expert in Markdown and HTML.

# App

You are building a desktop application that allows users to view Markdown files.

# Styling

- Use SCSS for styling.
- If you need icons, get them from iconoir. Use 2px line width.
- Never use rem for sizing. Use px instead. Use multiples of 8 or 4.
- Never use Tailwind CSS.

# Tech Stack

- Electron
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Markdown
- HTML

